Questions:

必须是下面这个顺序？如果反过来，‘new' 会被当成 ':id' 传进去，导致nil 错误！
get '/comments/new' do
  erb :'/comments/new'
end

get '/comments/:id' do
  @comment = Comment.first(:id => params[:id])
  erb :'/comments/show'
end